{"tid":2345134,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"自稱政協當街揮鋤頭 審訊期間潛逃 缺席聆訊下被判罪成囚一年","createTime":"2020-12-29T09:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T12:53:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3b036a0cecaf7fff4ea8dd1c5f33f439a02dc553","tid":2345134,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:17:23.000Z","msg":"去年8月5日大三罷，旺角有群眾聚集，當晚有自稱「做過政協」的六旬退休漢聲稱遭示威者包圍，拿起地上鐵鋤揮動，揚言自衞。他被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，早前受審期間棄保潛逃。裁判官林子勤認為無限期押後案件不符公義，今在被告缺席下作出裁決，裁定被告罪成，指他當晚手持鋤頭多次追向手無寸鐵的市民，更向記者揚言「今晚去衝佢、撞佢，我鋤佢老味」，無疑有傷人意圖，最終判他入獄一年。<br />\n<br />\n案件原定於上月3日進行結案陳詞，惟被告缺席聆訊，林官將案押後至同月6日，辯方稱被告家人、律師代表及警察均無法聯絡被告，林官遂向他發出拘捕令。林官其後去信控辯雙方，認為無限期押後案件不符公義，決定在被告缺席下繼續聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n案件今午裁決，被告沒有律師代表，其胞弟則派律師旁聽裁決。林官指出，本案關鍵證據是《米報》當晚所拍攝的片段，片中男子自稱朱木源，在港鐵太子站外手持鋤頭接受記者訪問，表達對示威者影響生活的不滿，揚言「今晚去衝佢、撞佢，我鋤呢班影響我生活嘅人、我鋤佢老味」，並示範將鋤頭鋤向地面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201229/BDQUPKDZCRD47AESRSDIV34IJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201229%2FBDQUPKDZCRD47AESRSDIV34IJI%2F&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=884ce0b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201229%2FBDQUPKDZCRD47AESRSDIV34IJI%2F&h=45badab6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201229/BDQUPKDZCRD47AESRSDIV34IJI/</a>"},{"pid":"af6d18f086338c238a3de7a0d5bdf848982426e2","tid":2345134,"uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"翻查網上資料，被告是香港廣東汕尾市同鄉總會常務副會長。"},{"pid":"ea263357a8c7832414d45b00d80ed77e82aebb54","tid":2345134,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f47111ef127aa8e1dedf53c1de5b0f1c4d9f82","tid":2345134,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:20:22.000Z","msg":"今晚去衝佢、撞佢，我鋤呢班影響我生活嘅人、我鋤佢老味<br />\n<br />\n斷正"},{"pid":"cac4f7117d5cc0047e51930108dc5e1b05ab3cda","tid":2345134,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea263357a8c7832414d45b00d80ed77e82aebb54","tid":2345134,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9a4477680a2dcec74763493e03e58ba80a5595","tid":2345134,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:22:15.000Z","msg":"依d藍屍打靶都哂子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc60e9cbd963f4a996d39a0b32cd80d74a6a29d","tid":2345134,"uid":235152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:22:20.000Z","msg":"斷正加走佬都係一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293dab3acb47404d338a5785dc97f53bb839ee0f","tid":2345134,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f47111ef127aa8e1dedf53c1de5b0f1c4d9f82","tid":2345134,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:20:22.000Z","msg":"今晚去衝佢、撞佢，我鋤呢班影響我生活嘅人、我鋤佢老味<br />\n<br />\n斷正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"石鏡泉 何妖？"},{"pid":"11c6fd872d63043f1448d3cc461da23ab6a94838","tid":2345134,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:23:56.000Z","msg":"咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7097da584899bca5a95f156fc1af79def98bc4b9","tid":2345134,"uid":46906,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:25:46.000Z","msg":"真逃犯天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gi