dBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:32:51.000Z","msg":"呢d就比林子勤"},{"pid":"a2150d8b64cf31982e800212b42215a2a235cd9b","tid":2345134,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:39:44.000Z","msg":"裁判官引述新聞片段，指被告曾稱「今晚衝佢撞佢」、「鋤呢班搞亂我哋生活嘅人」、「我鋤佢老味」，在記者面前用鋤頭鋤地，追向途人及黑衣人。裁判官續指，被告多次高舉鋤頭，明顯有傷人意圖、絕非自衞，裁定罪名成立。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E6%9B%BE%E4%BB%BB%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E6%BC%A2%E9%81%AD%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D-%E6%8C%81%E9%8B%A4%E9%A0%AD%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-%E5%AE%98-%E6%98%8E%E9%A1%AF%E6%9C%89%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA%E6%84%8F%E5%9C%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%2581%25B2%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2597%25AC%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%25B7%259D-%25E6%258C%2581%25E9%258B%25A4%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E6%2598%258E%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2582%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%259C%2596%2F&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=4ad6c0ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%2581%25B2%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2597%25AC%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%25B7%259D-%25E6%258C%2581%25E9%258B%25A4%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E6%2598%258E%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2582%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%259C%2596%2F&h=b802672c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E6%9B%BE%E4%BB%BB%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E6%BC%A2%E9%81%AD%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D-%E6%8C%81%E9%8B%A4%E9%A0%AD%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%9